com.skratchdot.electribe.fileexplorer.preferences

Class AddRemoveListFieldEditor

  • java.lang.Object
    • FieldEditor
      • com.skratchdot.electribe.fileexplorer.preferences.AddRemoveListFieldEditor

  • public class AddRemoveListFieldEditor
extends FieldEditor
    A field editor for displaying and storing a list of strings. Buttons are provided for adding items to the list and removing items from the list.
